    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a 1994 Mazda RX-7 (FD3S), a masterclass in lightweight engineering and high-revving performance. At its heart is the 13B-REW twin-rotor engine, featuring a sequential turbocharging system that delivers linear power and a seamless transition at 4,500 RPM. This example maintains its iconic 50/50 weight distribution and sophisticated four-wheel double-wishbone suspension, providing unparalleled feedback through the steering rack. The 5-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery out of corners. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul to manage the rotary's thermal demands and a comprehensive vacuum line 'rat's nest' inspection to ensure boost stability. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car, offering the visceral, analog experience that defined the golden era of JDM performance.",
      "price": 33500.0,
